{"tid":364585,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"請珍惜對你不離不棄既人，當佢冷淡你就會後悔莫及","createTime":"2017-08-18T13:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T01:36:03.000Z","uid":137741,"like":23,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1ae40af3cb9f3a0f4871d530291ee2cb074938b7","tid":364585,"uid":137741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T13:49:14.000Z","msg":"曾幾何時，總會有佢對我不離不棄<br />\n無論發生咩事，佢都會放棄自己既時間黎陪我、黎幫我<br />\n我發脾氣就開解我，我唔舒服就慰問我<br />\n畫畫比我、彈琴比我、帶我去睇日出、帶我去食好野<br />\n<br />\n不過，當我習慣左後就會覺得無論點樣佢都會繼續係我身邊<br />\n後尾先發現原來所有野，我都冇好好珍惜過<br />\n到最後，你既影子都漸漸淡出左佢既腦海中<br />\n其實我當時好鍾意佢，我又知道佢鍾意我<br />\n但我就一直拖，唔知點解一直拖，拖到佢都慢慢唔太再在意我啦<br />\n<br />\n如果有個人對你不離不棄，而你又覺得開心、有安全感既<br />\n真係要好好珍惜，唔好對人不理不睬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58fc2467648559a8757f5b9a71a943540255bac2","tid":364585,"uid":72345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:11:34.000Z","msg":"有時候習慣左就真係會覺得人地對你好係理所當然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望你之後會好好珍惜下一個對你好既人"},{"pid":"769d14cce7b277762c7924ab7a990813ec35a242","tid":364585,"uid":5921,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T15:05:52.000Z","msg":"抵死啦 臭閪"},{"pid":"a3ab03f743ff6690fed7c8364dd0393a647ec185","tid":364585,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:05:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"769661bde1b5ee1934206e1b95c185d26f0f4afe","tid":364585,"uid":137741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:22:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Timing？</blockquote><br />\n唔係 只係一直唔敢表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc181e711c7f6b7fafd630ec7db24649b122b0b","tid":364585,"uid":106967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T21:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa818a14d2b098085d64f51e0a37632c89ae914f","tid":364585,"uid":27210,"like